     3	The lab's code lineage descends from Morvan Zhou's train-robot-arm-from-
     4	scratch (Bilibili BV1nW411a7Qg, 2017): a hand-written analytic environment
     5	with `step(action) -> (s, r, done)`, `reset() -> s`, class-level
     6	state_dim/action_dim/action_bound, joint-increment actions, no simulator.
