    12	  - collision/termination accounting is CONTINUOUS-TIME EXACT (tau* via
    13	    godynur.continuous) — to our knowledge the first manipulator RL env
    14	    whose safety bookkeeping cannot tunnel;
    15	  - reward is switchable: 'uoar' (URPlanner Eq.12, discrete) vs 'ct'
